get {
  url: {{base_url}}/auth/me
  body: none
  auth: bearer
}

auth:bearer {
  token: {{access_token}}
}

docs {
  # Get Current User

  Retrieve the currently authenticated user's information.

  ## Authentication
  Requires a valid access token in the Authorization header.

  ## Response
  Returns the current user object with all user details.

  ## Note
  Make sure to login first to get a valid access_token.
}
